    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected without any hesitation. While the exterior is generally clean, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light wear on the driver's seat bolster consistent with careful use. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. This is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs necessary.",
