    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and appears as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, backed by a complete and documented service history. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in climate-controlled storage.",
